| Violent Crimes      | ~75.6              | ~20.1               | Men dominate violent crime statistics, including homicide and assault ([US DOJ, 2007](https://science.howstuffworks.com/life/inside-the-mind/emotions/men-more-violent.htm)) |
| Property Crimes     | Higher in males    | Significant in females | Women more involved in theft, fraud, and property-related offenses ([Vocativ, 2015](https://www.vocativ.com/usa/justice-usa/crimes-women-commit-most-often/index.html)) |
